  <summary date="2011-05-16T16:54:24Z" status="Introduced in House">10k Run for the Border Act - Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to increase employer civil fines for: (1) hiring, or recruiting or referring for a fee, an alien that the employer knows is not authorized for employment; and (2) continuing to employ such alien.

Sets forth a federal-state (and local) allocation of such additional penalty funds.</summary>
